research_municipality_step.notes: McLendon-Chisholm, TX operates under a Home Rule Charter with a Council-Manager form of government. The elected officials include a Mayor and six City Council members, with one Council Member also serving as Mayor Pro Tem. The 'Serving since' dates from October 2025 were used to determine the most current officials for Places 1 and 2, superseding earlier election results for those specific places.
